   Latitude/Longitude below specified in: [Geocentric]
   Year (from 1945 to 2005): 2001
   Altitude above the 1-Re surface (km) [from 0. to 40000.]: 100.__
   Latitude (degrees) [from -90. to -20. or from 20. to 90.]: 45.00_
   Longitude (degrees) [from 0. to 360.]: 270.0_

